concept.title: PSETUPIN Command
concept.shortdesc: Opens the Select Page Setup From File Dialog Box.

conbody.p: Open the Select to select a dwg, dwt, or dxf file from which to import page setups. After selecting the file and choosing Open, the Import Page Setups Dialog Box displays. It enables you to choose which page setups from the selected file you wish to import into the current drawing.
